              <tr> 
                <td class="chblue"><font class="h1font"> Advanced Decks</font></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td><table width="100%" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="3"><tr><td><font class="bfont"><table width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="4" cellspacing="0"><tr><td colspan="2"><font class="h1font">Control Freak (Need for Weave 4.0)</font></td></tr><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Rating</Font></TD><TD><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><img src="/magination/gfx/star3.gif" width="21" height="22" border="0" align="absmiddle"><font size=1>(4.50)</font> | <A HREF="/magination/decks/decks.php?reviews=22301">Read Reviews</A></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Author</font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> <A HREF="http://www.decktech.net/magination/main/mpage.php?member=9074">Rick "Ricohki" Garside</A></FONT> <font class="afont"> <a href='http://www.decktech.net/magination/main/mpage.php?member=9074&sub=1'> (Subscribe to this member)</a></font></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Description</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> This is the last version of the Need for Weave until Nightmare&#39;s Dawn comes out. It basically dominates the board with 2 different types of Magi, those who rely on attacking and those who rely on being attacked.</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Submitted</Font></TD><TD><font class="bfont"> March 21, 2002</FONT></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH="10%" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="h2font"> Cards</Font></TD><TD> </TD></TR><TR><TD COLSPAN="2" VALIGN="TOP"><font class="bfont"> Magi: <br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(516)">Gia</a><br>
(Starting: Book oes, <a href="javascript:card_browser(831)">Weave Powder</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(761}<a href="javascript:card_browser({842)">Bungaloo</a></a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(824}<a href="javascript:card_browser({516)">Gia</a>&#39;s Tome</a>)<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(818)">Kesia</a><br>
(Starting: <a href="javascript:card_browser(818)">Kesia</a>s Flute, <a href="javascript:card_browser(831)">Weave Powder</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(797)">Grass Hyren</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(837)">Sawgrass</a>)<br>
Bo&#39; asha<br>
(Starting: <a href="javascript:card_browser(804)">Pody</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(805)">Quallon</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(837)">Sawgrass</a>, <a href="javascript:card_browser(831)">Weave Powder</a>)<br>
<br>
Creatures:<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(797)">Grass Hyren</a>: 3<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(801)">Lascinth</a>: 3<br>
